X:49
T:Sing, O Sing, This Blessed Morn
C:Words: Christopher Wordsworth, 1865. Music: William Henry Monk, 1865.
C:SSAATTBB arr. for lever harp accompaniment, key C (no transposition).
C:Original: public domain / Open Hymnal Project, 2011 Revision.
M:4/4
L:1/4
Q:1/4=120
K:C
%%staves {(V1 V2) (V3 V4) (V5 V6) (V7 V8)}
